job.description:
The candidate must have SQL skills and must also have experience using Python or R. The analyst should be able to create strong, telling visualizations using a BI Tool, indicating possible areas of further investigation. Strong communication skills are a must, in order to help explain issues to the customer and provide possible solutions.&amp;nbsp;Data Scientist Required or Preferred Skills&amp;nbsp;  - Solid presentation skills.&amp;nbsp;   
  - Must have a Data Science Degree   
  - Must have neural network knowledge/experience   
  - Strong communication skills – able to give technical information in understandable terms.   
  - Able to interact easily with clients.   
  - SQL.&amp;nbsp;   
  - Python/R experience&amp;nbsp;   
  - Knows how to format and manipulate data.&amp;nbsp;   
  - Subject matter expertise in military maintenance data is preferred.&amp;nbsp;   
  - Experience in BI tools is preferred but not required.&amp;nbsp;   
  - Must be eager to learn and have an aptitude for thinking outside of the box.&amp;nbsp;   
  - Needs to be able to communicate ideas clearly and work in a collaborative environment.   
  - Must have a propensity collecting and analyzing data, and presenting results in a concise manner with minimal guidance.
